name: FMovieSceneTangentData
doc: Tangents for curve channel control points.

ArriveTangent: If RCIM_Cubic, the arriving tangent at this key
LeaveTangent: If RCIM_Cubic, the leaving tangent at this key
ArriveTangentWeight: If RCTWM_WeightedArrive or RCTWM_WeightedBoth, the weight of the left tangent
LeaveTangentWeight: If RCTWM_WeightedLeave or RCTWM_WeightedBoth, the weight of the right tangent
TangentWeightMode: If RCIM_Cubic, the tangent weight mode
